      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just a dull ache though, not like a migraine or anything. i dont want to deal with the hassle of calling my doctor just for a headache. if i just take like one or two pills, it shouldn't affect my kidney numbers at all right? i really need the pain to go away so i can focus.",
